    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s practically perfect. It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014kept in a climate-controlled garage, detailed every month, and it still has that 'fresh off the lot' smell! It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
