    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one, maintaining its original factory luster. The exterior paint is flawless, treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights the deep, mirror-like finish\u2014absolutely no swirls, rock chips, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin retains that signature new-car scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every tactile surface feels as crisp as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete binder of records included. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage remains free of any road debris or oxidation. This isn't just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
